1
00:00:00,667 --> 00:00:02,234
Zhou Youzhi.

2
00:00:02,235 --> 00:00:03,736
At school,

3
00:00:03,737 --> 00:00:05,604
all you ever think about is studying

4
00:00:05,605 --> 00:00:07,007
and Chen Tianyou.

5
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:09,275
Ever since he said he wasn't coming back,

6
00:00:09,809 --> 00:00:11,544
you've been like the walking dead.

7
00:00:12,512 --> 00:00:14,414
I've really had enough.

8
00:00:15,181 --> 00:00:16,649
Let's break up.

9
00:00:28,828 --> 00:00:30,096
I actually hope

10
00:00:31,030 --> 00:00:33,366
you never find this recording.

11
00:00:34,234 --> 00:00:35,300
That way, I won't have to worry

12
00:00:35,301 --> 00:00:36,469
about what you'd think of me,

13
00:00:37,570 --> 00:00:39,672
or wish for you to accept me.

14
00:00:40,573 --> 00:00:42,375
Remember the day the
college results came out?

15
00:00:42,909 --> 00:00:44,029
I was going to steal a kiss,

16
00:00:44,744 --> 00:00:45,812
but then you woke up.

17
00:00:47,013 --> 00:00:48,748
I really wanted to just ask you:

18
00:00:49,749 --> 00:00:51,870
If you know what I was doing,
why didn't you push me away?

19
00:00:53,586 --> 00:00:54,820
Didn't you realize

20
00:00:54,821 --> 00:00:56,823
my feelings for you
weren't just as a friend?

21
00:00:59,359 --> 00:01:00,359
But I couldn't.

22
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:02,262
I didn't even have the guts to ask.

23
00:01:03,396 --> 00:01:04,763
I used to think

24
00:01:04,764 --> 00:01:06,199
we might actually have a chance.

25
00:01:07,734 --> 00:01:09,536
You were so dependent on me,

26
00:01:10,336 --> 00:01:12,305
and you never pulled
away when I touched you.

27
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,742
But once you got a girlfriend,

28
00:01:16,176 --> 00:01:17,310
I backed off.

29
00:01:18,545 --> 00:01:19,845
I didn't have the courage

30
00:01:19,846 --> 00:01:21,781
to stand by your side like she does,

31
00:01:22,482 --> 00:01:23,782
or let you openly

32
00:01:23,783 --> 00:01:25,218
tell everyone who we are.

33
00:01:27,821 --> 00:01:29,055
We only met

34
00:01:29,689 --> 00:01:31,057
because our names were so similar.

35
00:01:32,091 --> 00:01:33,559
But the person in your heart,

36
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,060
the one looking back at you...

37
00:01:35,061 --> 00:01:37,130
it won't be me. It shouldn't be me.

38
00:01:38,198 --> 00:01:39,198
So,

39
00:01:39,966 --> 00:01:42,235
I'll just stay by your side in secret.

40
00:02:59,179 --> 00:03:00,313
You have to be okay.

41
00:03:00,847 --> 00:03:03,883
Only then will I be okay, too.
